   </prolog>
   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Open Microsoft Word. If you have already downloaded the document from Salesforce or another location, open the document in Word. Otherwise, choose a blank document.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Go to <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Insert</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>My Add-ins</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Apttus X-Author</uicontrol>
               </menucascade>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="../logging_in_to_x_author_co_45711457/45711457.xml" format="dita">Log in to X-Author Contracts</xref>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <uicontrol>(Document currently open in Word) </uicontrol>The document is
               automatically checked out and locked by you (you will see a message).</p>
            <p>
               <note id="note_fhf_lx3_12c">
                  <p>If the document is already checked out by another user, you will not be able to
                     work with the document until it is checked in or the lock is released. </p>
                  <p>See <xref href="../locking_and_unlocking_doc_45220101/45220101.xml" format="dita">Locking and Unlocking Documents</xref> for more
                     information.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>(No Document open) Click on the <uicontrol>List Agreements</uicontrol> icon to
               switch to a tab view of all agreement records you have permission to access.</p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image height="400"
                         placement="break"
                         href="../attachments/45220108/49676302.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>(No Document open) Scroll through the list of agreements or use the
                  <uicontrol>Search</uicontrol> tool at the top to search for your agreement record
               by keyword(s).</p>
            <p>Click the <image placement="inline"
                      width="20"
                      href="../attachments/45220108/49676303.png"
                      id="image_hlg_rx3_12c"/> icon to view
               additional details about the agreement.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <uicontrol>(No Document open) </uicontrol>Click the <uicontrol>List
                  Documents</uicontrol> button to the right of the agreement record name to display
               a list of document versions attached to that record. </p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image height="400"
                         placement="break"
                         href="../attachments/45220108/49676304.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <uicontrol>(No Document open)</uicontrol> Click the <uicontrol>Download
                  Document</uicontrol> button to the right of the agreement version you want to work
               with.</p>
            <stepresult>
               <p>The Document Version is downloaded to your computer.</p>
            </stepresult>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Open the downloaded document in Word. </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>You will see the message "Document is locked by you." </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
      <result id="result_nwl_b2q_12c">
         <p>All menu options are enabled. </p>
